Description:

It's Sant Jordi! (Saint George's Day — a Catalan tradition where people gift books and roses)
Roses and books for everyone!
Create a program that gives you a random gift:

You choose if you want a book or a rose
There are 5 possible books (each with a title)
There are 5 possible roses (each with a color)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Program:

To try this program, just run: "php YourFileDirectory/SantJordi.php" on the terminal!